    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and documented. The overall credibility evidence, including N=11 specimen validation across two independent laboratories with all quantitative acceptance criteria met, is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5mm pedicle screw compression-bending COU at medium model risk level.",
